  Release Info:
  ~~~~~~~~~~~~~

  Set directly after the events of 2014's Oddworld: New æN' Tasty,
  Oddworld: Soulstorm is the second game in Abe's heroic new epic. 

  Abe has now undergone a transformation - from a clueless Mudokon cog
  about to be chewed up by the Glukkons' mega-corporate machines into an
  unlikely hero who rises to become a beacon of hope.


